modify the default key value under `~/.password-store/.gpg-id`. for example in my case it is

``` bash
F5190B59F4E143E0
```

you can [[Get GPG Key Id]] if you don't know your key id.

now [[Reencrypt Pass Password Store With Different GPG Key]]
